= Connect four

Console based "Vier gewinnt".

== Game play

playerx> 2

 12345678
 ........
 ........
 ........
 ........
 ........
 ........
 ..xoox..
 .xxoox x


playero> 4

 12345678
 ........
 ........
 ........
 ........
 ........
 ...o....
 ..xoox..
 .xxoox x



== Test driven development (TDD) with test-unit

  rake test


== Enviornment

* ruby-1.9-3-p125
* rvm
** rvm install ruby-1.9.3
** rvm use 1.9.3
** ruby -v # => 1.9.3

* gems
** bundler # Gemfile
** rake    # Rakefile
** test-unit # -> minitest
